  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so there was contact, with money and bribing some people, and couriers, it was possible to take letters, and sometimes a small parcel, to the Jewish committee's headquarters, and then they would see to it that these would reach, and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was some communication at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was in the-- What do you remember that your father wrote?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall receiving from my father, but I do recall sending this article-- no, maybe he sent back-- it wasn't a long period of-- of exposure to this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're talking here-- the episode we're entering into, itself lasted maybe four to six weeks, so there wasn't much time to establish patterns.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the pattern that did-- we did have that at least once a week, we used to go from where we lived, which was in the gentile side, to the heart of the very, very, almost Jewish ghetto side, where most of the Orthodox Jews lived.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that's where also the office of the Jewish Council was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where we used to take whatever we were sending to my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was to cross the park in the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there's a-- there's a nice central park in the city of Antwerp, and we were-- where we lived, and at our business in the non-Jewish part, was on one side of the park, and the Jewish was-- area was exactly on the opposite side of the park.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] New chapter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very bad memories on that particular day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On that particular day, my mother, and my brother, and I walked towards that office where we're going to deliver what we want to send to my father.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
